body.description: Protect a baby's delicate skin from wetness with Comfees Unisex Baby Diapers. Designed with the Comfees Total Fit System, this product provides maximum comfort and prevents leaks between changes. Comfees premium diapers have a contoured shape, with a SoftFlex waistband and stretchy, tab closures for a snug fit that moves the way a baby does. Comfees disposable diapers have a soft breathable cloth-like outer layer with an allergen-free liner. The super absorbent core features DriNite protection for up to 12 hours for restful bedtime. These size 5 Comfees baby diapers are made without perfumes, and have a kid-friendly design. The nonwoven top sheet offers more stability for movement and confidence. - Comfees diapers feature the Comfees Total Fit System that stops leaks to keep babies dry. The SoftFlex designed for a flexible waistband and stretchy tabs to fit with security and comfort. Comfees premium diapers move naturally with a baby's body for fun and play. The diaper has a soft breathable cloth-like outside with an absorbent core and a soft inside liner to prevent allergic reactions . These size 5 Comfees baby diapers provide DriNite protection for up to 12 hours so babies can sleep at night. This disposable product is unscented and decorated with a colorful kid design for enjoyment and encouragement.
